FBIS4-60912 "drsov084_b_94043" FBIS-SOV-94-084 Daily Report 30 Apr 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Military & Space Issues Production of Tu-160 Strategic Aircraft Discontinued Production of Tu-160 Strategic Aircraft Discontinued LD3004120994 Moscow 2x2 Television in Russian 1030 GMT 30 Apr 94 LD3004120994 Moscow 2x2 Television Russian BFN [Text] The Gorbunov Aviation Association in Kazan has discontinued production of the strategic missile-carrying Tu-160 [Tupolev] aircraft. As a RIA correspondent was told at the association's directorate, production was discontinued by direct instruction of the Russian president.
